<m0>Court resolves issue<ql>
on redistricting route<ql>
<m1><styl>vs,4 <styl>txt,11p1 <styl>ragx<ql>
<styl>indentl,2l,0,4l,3.5p<ql>
<styl>txt,11p1<ql>
